{
  "html": "<div id=\"BUV\" class=\"uplift front\">\n    <section id=\"course-front-body\" class=\"responsive-padding\" style=\"color: #2d3b45; background: none; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px;\">\n        <article id=\"course-lesson-intro-text\" style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">\n            <h3 class=\"heavy\" style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 2.7em;\">Quality Assurance</h3>\n            <p>The Quality Assurance course, developed by BUV\u2019s Academic Quality Office (AQO), acts as a central reservoir of information for faculty. It provides vital resources on academic monitoring, peer observation, faculty development, assessment approval, and moderation, promoting academic excellence through robust quality assurance and continuous improvement.</p>\n        </article>\n        <div class=\"grid-row\">\n            <article class=\"col-lg-4 buv-responsive-video-100\" style=\"padding-left: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px;\"><iframe class=\"lti-embed\" style=\"display: inline-block; border: none;\" title=\"OB introduction video\" src=\"https://buv.instructuremedia.com/embed/95ee6031-235a-47b6-a79d-7acac10191fd\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"webkitallowfullscreen\" mozallowfullscreen=\"mozallowfullscreen\" allow=\"geolocation *; microphone *; camera *; midi *; encrypted-media *; autoplay *; clipboard-write *; display-capture *\" data-studio-resizable=\"true\" data-studio-tray-enabled=\"true\" data-studio-convertible-to-link=\"true\"></iframe></article>\n            <article class=\"col-lg-8\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; padding-left: 12px;\">\n                <h3><strong>Learning Objectives for this module:</strong></h3>\n                <details style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Ensuring Assurance of Learning</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Establishing and mapping the learning outcomes to ensure students' assurance of learning.</p>\n                </details>\n                <hr>\n                <details>\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Recording and Maintaining Academic Quality Records</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Keeping accurate and comprehensive records to ensure compliance and continuous improvement.</p>\n                </details>\n                <hr>\n                <details>\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Teaching Observations through Peer Pair Observation</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Encouraging collaborative teaching development through structured peer observations.</p>\n                </details>\n                <hr>\n                <details>\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Academic Development and Teaching Qualification Pathway</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Providing faculty members with opportunities for professional growth with HEA fellowship support.</p>\n                </details>\n                <hr>\n                <details>\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Ensuring Assessment Approval and Marking Moderation</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Overseeing assessment validation and moderation to maintain academic integrity and fairness.</p>\n                </details>\n                <hr>\n                <details>\n                    <summary style=\"cursor: pointer; display: block;\"><strong>+ Supporting Institutional Accreditations and Rankings</strong></summary>\n                    <p><span style=\"color: #ba372a; font-size: 14pt;\">+ &nbsp;</span>Assisting in accreditations such as QAA and QS rankings to ensure compliance and elevate the institution\u2019s global standing.</p>\n                </details>\n            </article>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid-row responsive-padding\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -50px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"padding-left: 12px;\"><strong>Module Content:</strong></h3>\n</div>",
